seeds.target: Tengo miedo de que olvides por qué necesitábamos quedarnos aquí.
seeds.known: I'm afraid that you'll forget why we needed to stay here.

seeds.target: Acordemos que fue estúpido decir la verdad.
seeds.known: Let's agree that it was stupid to tell the truth.

seeds.target: En lugar de dar una excusa.
seeds.known: Instead of giving an excuse.

seeds.target: Te llamaré de vuelta en tres o cuatro minutos.
seeds.known: I'll call you back in three or four minutes.

seeds.target: Para comprobar si has podido terminar.
seeds.known: To check if you've been able to finish.

seeds.target: Me resulta difícil creer que no puedes adivinar.
seeds.known: I'm finding it hard to believe that you can't guess.

seeds.target: Adivina quién me contó esa historia graciosa.
seeds.known: Guess who told me that funny story.

seeds.target: Probablemente se supone que debo guardar esas cosas en otra habitación.
seeds.known: I'm probably supposed to keep those things in another room.

seeds.target: ¿Pueden todos levantar las manos?
seeds.known: Can you all put your hands up?

seeds.target: Para que pueda contarlas
seeds.known: So I can count them

seeds.target: No es verdad que cualquiera pueda ganar el juego.
seeds.known: It isn't true that anyone can win the game.

seeds.target: A menos que tengan suerte.
seeds.known: Unless they're lucky.

seeds.target: No escuchará cada palabra que dices.
seeds.known: She won't listen to every word you say.

seeds.target: No vayamos afuera con este clima espantoso.
seeds.known: Let's not go outside in this dreadful weather.

seeds.target: Hizo una promesa de que no elegiría el trabajo equivocado.
seeds.known: He made a promise that he wouldn't choose the wrong job.

seeds.target: Solía pensar que ser loco era malo.
seeds.known: I used to think that being crazy was bad.

seeds.target: Pero estaba equivocado.
seeds.known: But I was wrong.

seeds.target: No quiero parecer como si no me importara.
seeds.known: I don't want to seem as though I don't care.

seeds.target: Pero se está haciendo tarde.
seeds.known: But it's getting late.

seeds.target: No me importa si quieres irte sin el coche.
seeds.known: I don't mind if you want to leave without the car.
